{
  "stem": "13874.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Once Hitler came to-- into power, to keep such a tight lid on his own people, he needed lots of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was-- it wasn't just a few people on top who said, do that and that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were hordes of henchmen who had to be there-- volunteers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the biggest shame of the Germans is that Germany was able to have so many henchmen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And even nowadays, they don't talk about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "For everybody in Germany, whatever they thought, to some extent were-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --involved.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I-- I can't think of the word.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so that's interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they don't-- nobody wants to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't talk about it before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't talk about it afterwards, because their neighbors also lived in-- lived-- they had to still live with neighbors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't know who was who.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it became-- it was hushed up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that is probably the last one-- is the basis on which some claim that the Holocaust never existed, because you hear the stories only from non-Germans.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But that has to be considered, and it's very easy to say that the Germans who set out all, or not all, or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The biggest crime, as I see, is what the Germans did with themself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because it was-- not worse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did suffer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was-- for a German-- it was more insidious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And actually, that is a message we should portray, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the way it really was inside Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- it-- we were maybe-- the Jews-- were the last act in the big drama.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were other acts just as bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And just to see this-- and they may come again.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
